<template>
  <MainPage v-if="currentPage === 'main'"/>
  <ProductPage v-else-if="currentPage === 'product'"/>
  <NotPage v-else/>
</template>

<script>
import MainPage from './pages/MainPage.vue';
import ProductPage from './pages/ProductPage.vue';
import NotPage from './pages/NotPage.vue';

export default {
  name: 'App',
  data() {
    return {
      currentPage: 'main',
    }
  },
  components: {
    MainPage,
    ProductPage,
    NotPage,
  }
}
</script>

<style>
</style>
